  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6604.83 sitting just below the massive GEX flip at 6610 (+76.3B), dealers are positioned to aggressively sell any push through 6610 while providing support around current levels given the PIN regime. The 35.3% surge in 1-minute GEX change suggests heavy gamma positioning is building, creating a tight range between 6590 (max negative gamma where dealers amplify selling) and 6610 (max positive gamma where dealers cap upside). Watch for mean reversion behavior with dealers providing natural resistance at 6610/6605 positive gamma walls and accelerated selling if we break below 6590.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect price to get pinned between 6590-6610 with limited upside past 6610.",
